<L>__{interior kitchen day}
<A>__{he is putting groceries away as she rolls into the room. he doesn't look at her, tries to be casual, but his thoughts are bubbling out.}
<C>__{catch}
<D>__{you know the cop the woman cop? she... visited me.}
